'''有甲目'''（[[學名|學名]]：{{lang|la |Cingulata}}）或稱 '''帶甲目'''，是產自[[美洲|美洲]]的一類披甲[[哺乳动物|哺乳动物]]，隸屬[[有胎盤類|有胎盤類]]的[[異關節總目|異關節總目]]，在舊時的分類體系中則被歸為[[貧齒目|貧齒目]]的[[亞目|亞目]]。現存種類統稱為[[犰狳|犰狳]]，分屬兩[[科_(生物)|科]]：[[犰狳科|犰狳科]]與[[倭犰狳科|倭犰狳科]]<ref name = MSW3>{{MSW3| id = 11700001}}</ref>，體型普遍較小。另有一支在 1.2 萬年前[[更新世|更新世]]末滅絕的[[潘帕獸科|潘帕獸科]]，該科物種體重可達 200 kg<ref name = "Vizcaíno">{{cite journal | last = Vizcaíno | first = S. F. | last2 = De Iuliis | first2 = G. | last3 = Bargo     | first3 = M. S. | title = Skull Shape, Masticatory Apparatus, and Diet of ''Vassallia'' and ''Holmesina'' (Mammalia: Xenarthra: Pampatheriidae): When Anatomy Constrains Destiny | journal = Journal of Mammalian Evolution | volume = 5 | issue = 4 | pages = 291–322 | year = 1998 | url = http://www.springerlink.com/content/p20042452ll557v1/ | doi = 10.1023/A:1020500127041 | accessdate = 2011-10-20 }}{{Dead link|date=2020年2月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>，遠大於現存最大的有甲目——[[大犰狳|大犰狳]]（45 kg）<ref>[http://www.faunaparaguay.com/mamm6Priodontesmaximus.pdf Giant Armadillo ''Priodontes maximus'' (Kerr, 1792)] {{Wayback|url=http://www.faunaparaguay.com/mamm6Priodontesmaximus.pdf |date=20131029201209 }}.) FaunaParaguay.com</ref>。此外倭犰狳科中滅絕於[[末次冰期|末次冰期]]的[[雕齒獸亞科|雕齒獸亞科]]物種，體重更可達 2000 kg<ref name="Blanco2009">{{cite journal|last1=Blanco|first1=R. E.|last2=Jones|first2=W. W. |last3=Rinderknecht|first3=A.|title=The sweet spot of a biological hammer: the centre of percussion of glyptodont (Mammalia: Xenarthra) tail clubs|journal=Proceedings of the Royal Society B: Biological Sciences|volume=276|issue=1675|date=2009-08-26|pages=3971–3978|issn=0962-8452|doi=10.1098/rspb.2009.1144}}</ref>以上。

有甲目發源於[[古新世|古新世]]的[[南美洲|南美洲]]，在 300 萬年前[[巴拿馬地峽|巴拿馬地峽]]形成後的[[南北美洲生物大遷徙|南北美洲生物大遷徙]]中，其三個科均有部分物種向北擴散<ref name = "Mead_2007">{{cite journal | last = Mead | first = J. I. | author2 = Swift, S. L. | author3 = White, R. S. | author4 = McDonald, H. G. | author5 = Baez, A. | title = Late Pleistocene (Rancholabrean) Glyptodont and Pampathere (Xenarthra, Cingulata) from Sonora, Mexico | journal = [[Revista_Mexicana_de_Ciencias_Geológicas|Revista Mexicana de Ciencias Geológicas]] | volume = 24 | issue = 3 | pages = 439–449 (see p. 440) | publisher =  | location =  | year = 2007 | url = http://www.scielo.org.mx/pdf/rmcg/v24n3/v24n3a11.pdf | doi =  | accessdate = 2013-06-15 | archive-date = 2017-08-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170814164019/http://www.scielo.org.mx/pdf//rmcg/v24n3/v24n3a11.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Woodburne2010">{{cite journal|last1=Woodburne|first1=M. O.|title=The Great American Biotic Interchange: Dispersals, Tectonics, Climate, Sea Level and Holding Pens|journal=Journal of Mammalian Evolution|volume= 17|issue= 4|date= 2010-07-14|pages= 245–264 (see p. 249)|issn= 1064-7554|doi= 10.1007/s10914-010-9144-8|pmid=21125025|pmc=2987556}}</ref>，而多數大型種類都在[[全新世|全新世]][[古印第安人|古印第安人]]殖民美洲不久後滅絕<ref name="HubbeHubbe2013">{{cite journal|last1=Hubbe|first1=A.|last2=Hubbe|first2=M.|last3=Neves|first3=W. A.|title=The Brazilian megamastofauna of the Pleistocene/Holocene transition and its relationship with the early human settlement of the continent|journal=Earth-Science Reviews|volume=118|date=March 2013|pages=1–10 (see pages 3, 6)|issn=0012-8252|doi=10.1016/j.earscirev.2013.01.003}}</ref><ref name = "Fiedal">{{Cite book | first = Stuart | last = Fiedal | author-link =  | editor-last = Haynes | editor-first = Gary | contribution = Sudden Deaths: The Chronology of Terminal Pleistocene Megafaunal Extinction | contribution-url = http://www.springerlink.com/content/l225628681672725/?p=5af1eb7387d443a2b514b284c646efa7&pi=1 | title = American Megafaunal Extinctions at the End of the Pleistocene | year = 2009 | pages = 21–37 (see p. 31) | place =  | publisher = [[Springer_Science+Business_Media|Springer]] | url = http://www.springerlink.com/content/978-1-4020-8792-9 | doi = 10.1007/978-1-4020-8793-6_2 | isbn = 978-1-4020-8792-9 | oclc = 313368423 | access-date = 2015-04-11 | archive-url = https://archive.is/20121205074031/http://www.springerlink.com/content/978-1-4020-8792-9 | archive-date = 2012-12-05 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。

==主要特征==
有甲目物種的背部有細小的、呈鱗片狀、[[角質|角質化]]的重疊表皮，稱為“{{le|鱗甲|Scute}}”（scute），由[[皮內成骨|皮膚骨化]]（osteoderm）形成，並成為其獨有的背甲。大多數物種在肩部及臀部亦有堅實的護盾，並有三到九條以具彈性皮膚分隔開的鱗甲帶覆蓋其側面和底部。<ref name="EoM">{{cite book |editor=Macdonald, D. |author=Dickman, Christopher R. |year=1984 |title=The Encyclopedia of Mammals |url=https://archive.org/details/encyclopediaofma00mals_0 |publisher=Facts on File |location=New York |pages=[https://archive.org/details/encyclopediaofma00mals_0/page/781 781]–783 |isbn=0-87196-871-1}}</ref>。

潘帕獸的甲殼仍有一定的活動空間，這是由於甲殼之間仍有三條可動的橫向皮膚骨化帶。<ref name = "Vizcaíno"/>但與犰狳不同，這些帶是由單一的鱗甲所覆蓋，而不是像犰狳般是由多於一條鱗甲帶所連接。<ref name = "Vizcaíno"/>雕齒獸的背甲像龜的甲殼般，是由已融合的骨板所組成，完全沒有可動的鱗甲帶。

潘帕獸和犰狳均有鱗甲覆蓋於其頭部之上。雕齒獸則擁有被鱗甲厚實包覆的尾部，甚至如[[星尾獸|星尾獸]]在尾巴的末端擁有尾槌，就如同[[恐龍|恐龍]]中的[[甲龍亞目|甲龍亞目]]。證據顯示這些尾槌可以用來防禦或是雄性間競爭。<ref name="Blanco2009" />

許多種犰狳以[[昆蟲|昆蟲]]或其他無脊椎動物為食；部分種類為[[雜食性|雜食性]]，以小型脊椎動物與植物為食。潘帕獸則認為是以啃食地面植披為主<ref name = "Vizcaíno"/>而同位素分析顯示雕齒獸是以 [[C4類二氧化碳固定|C4]] 類[[禾本科|禾本科]]為主食。<ref name="Pérez-CrespoArroyo-Cabrales2011">{{cite journal|last1=Pérez-Crespo|first1=V. A.|last2=Arroyo-Cabrales|first2=J.|last3=Alva-Valdivia|first3=L. M.|last4=Morales-Puente|first4=P.|last5=Cienfuegos-Alvarado|first5=E.|title=Diet and habitat definitions for Mexican glyptodonts from Cedral (San Luis Potosí, México) based on stable isotope analysis|journal=Geological Magazine|volume=149|issue=01|date=2011-10-18|pages=153–157|issn=0016-7568|doi=10.1017/S0016756811000951}}</ref>另外[[六帶犰狳亞科|六帶犰狳亞科]]中已滅絕的{{le|巨六帶犰狳屬|Macroeuphractus}}較為特別，為特化的[[肉食性動物|肉食性動物]]。

==下級分類==
[[File:Gyptodon_Cosmo_Caixa.JPG|thumb]]{{le|荷氏獸屬|Holmesina}}下的一種（''Holmesina septentrionalis''），藏於{{le|巴塞羅那宇宙科學館|CosmoCaixa Barcelona}}。]]
[[File:Nine-banded_armadillo_skeleton.jpg|thumb]]（''Dasypus novemcinctus''）的骨骼模型，藏於[[美国国立自然历史博物馆|美国国立自然历史博物馆]]。]]
[[File:Glyptodon_clavipes_01.jpg|thumb]]的[[模式種|模式種]]（''Glyptodon clavipes''），藏於[[柏林自然博物館|柏林自然博物館]]。]]
以下分類反映了有甲目的[[種系發生|種系發生]]研究結果（Delsuc 等人，2016）。傳統分類認為[[雕齒獸|雕齒獸]]是一個獨立於現代犰狳之外的[[演化支|演化支]]，但對[[星尾獸|星尾獸]]的 [[mtDNA|mtDNA]] 進行分析發現，星尾獸原本所屬的[[雕齒獸亞科|雕齒獸亞科]]與現存的[[倭犰狳亞科|倭犰狳亞科]]及[[三帶犰狳亞科|三帶犰狳亞科]]是同一演化支上的[[姐妹群|姐妹群]]<ref name="Delsuc2016">{{cite journal|last1=Delsuc|first1=F.|last2=Gibb|first2=G. C.|last3=Kuch|first3=M.|last4=Billet|first4=G.|last5=Hautier|first5=L.|last6=Southon|first6=J.|last7=Rouillard|first7=J.-M.|last8=Fernicola|first8=J. C.|last9=Vizcaíno|first9=S. F.|last10=MacPhee|first10=R. D.E.|last11=Poinar|first11=H. N.|title=The phylogenetic affinities of the extinct glyptodonts|journal=Current Biology|volume=26|issue=4|date=2016-02-22|pages=R155–R156|doi=10.1016/j.cub.2016.01.039}}</ref>。

